long_description: The OnGuard Doberman cable and keyed padlock provides light-duty security for your bicycle, all in a flexible, budget-friendly package. 8mm self-coiling cable is light and compact and has permanent loops for easy locking; vinyl coating helps protect your bike's finish. Padlock is constructed out of laminated steel with smooth brass lock mechanism internals and a 8mm hardened steel shackle. Comes with 5 heavy-duty, F-style keys. OnGuard rates this lock as a 30 out of 100 on their 100-point security rating system, where higher-rated locks offer increased security.
